Author: elijahdmmt
Text: thanks for the response 🙌🏻, ah ik what my friends will think abt it, even if they don’t say it, i don’t want anyone to know it’s weird, i’ve never felt this way about my mental health before :/

Author: jcsxx
Text: Please get help right away and talk to your friends who are going / have gone through it. They won’t say you’re copying them and they’ll know ways to help you cope and they can talk to you about therapy and whatever else. You definitely need help, you deserve help, please don’t feel guilty about getting it 💗
